protected void decodeValue(java.lang.String valueString)
Rebuild the value derived values based on the unparsed value field. The unparsed value field is assumed to have the following fields in order. 0*) valueList 1) propertyDefinitionName

decodeValue

protected void decodeValue(java.lang.String valueString,
                           com.cboe.interfaces.domain.property.PropertyDefinitionGroup definitions)
Rebuild the value derived values based on the unparsed value field. The unparsed value field is assumed to have the following fields in order. 0*) valueList 1) propertyDefinitionName The last field parsed will only be assumed to be a propertyDefinitionName if the value begins with "@". In addition, if the property definition group is not null, the method will try to attach a property definition to this property.
